<div class="chapter ch7" data-usfm="PSA.7">
  <div class="label">7</div>
  <div class="s">
    <span class="heading">为公义而祈祷</span>
  </div>
  <div class="d">
    <span class="content">大卫指着便雅悯人古实的话，向耶和华唱的流离歌。</span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="content"> </span><span class="verse v1" data-usfm="PSA.7.1"><span class="label">1</span><span
      class="content">耶和华—我的 神啊，我投靠你！</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v1" data-usfm="PSA.7.1"><span class="content">求你救我脱离一切追赶我的人，将我救拔出来！</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v1" data-usfm="PSA.7.1"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v2"
      data-usfm="PSA.7.2"><span class="label">2</span><span class="content">恐怕他们像狮子撕裂我，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v2" data-usfm="PSA.7.2"><span class="content">甚至撕碎，无人搭救。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="b"></div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v2" data-usfm="PSA.7.2"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v3"
      data-usfm="PSA.7.3"><span class="label">3</span><span class="content">耶和华—我的 神啊，我若行了这事，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v3" data-usfm="PSA.7.3"><span class="content">若有罪孽在我手里，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v3" data-usfm="PSA.7.3"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v4"
      data-usfm="PSA.7.4"><span class="label">4</span><span class="content">我若以恶报那与我交好的人—</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v4" data-usfm="PSA.7.4"><span class="content">连那无故与我为敌的，我也救了他，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v4" data-usfm="PSA.7.4"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v5"
      data-usfm="PSA.7.5"><span class="label">5</span><span class="content">就任凭仇敌追赶我，直到追上，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v5" data-usfm="PSA.7.5"><span class="content">将我的性命踏在地下，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v5" data-usfm="PSA.7.5"><span class="content">使我的荣耀归于灰尘。 </span><span class="qs"><span
        class="content">（细拉） </span></span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="b"></div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v5" data-usfm="PSA.7.5"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v6"
      data-usfm="PSA.7.6"><span class="label">6</span><span class="content">耶和华啊，求你在怒中起来，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v6" data-usfm="PSA.7.6"><span class="content">挺身而立，抵挡我敌人的暴怒！</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v6" data-usfm="PSA.7.6"><span class="content">求你为我兴起！你已经命定施行审判！</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v6" data-usfm="PSA.7.6"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v7"
      data-usfm="PSA.7.7"><span class="label">7</span><span class="content">愿众民的会环绕你！</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v7" data-usfm="PSA.7.7"><span class="content">愿你从其上归于高位！</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v7" data-usfm="PSA.7.7"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v8"
      data-usfm="PSA.7.8"><span class="label">8</span><span class="content">耶和华向众民施行审判；</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v8" data-usfm="PSA.7.8"><span class="content">耶和华啊，求你按我的公义和我心中的纯正判断我。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="b"></div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v8" data-usfm="PSA.7.8"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v9"
      data-usfm="PSA.7.9"><span class="label">9</span><span class="content">愿恶人的恶断绝！</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v9" data-usfm="PSA.7.9"><span class="content">愿你坚立义人！</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v9" data-usfm="PSA.7.9"><span class="content">因为公义的 神察验人的心肠肺腑。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v9" data-usfm="PSA.7.9"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v10"
      data-usfm="PSA.7.10"><span class="label">10</span><span class="content"> 神是我的盾牌；</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v10" data-usfm="PSA.7.10"><span class="content">他拯救心里正直的人。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v10" data-usfm="PSA.7.10"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v11"
      data-usfm="PSA.7.11"><span class="label">11</span><span class="content"> 神是公义的审判者，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v11" data-usfm="PSA.7.11"><span class="content">又是天天</span><span class="add"><span
        class="content">向恶人</span></span><span class="content">发怒的 神。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="b"></div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v11" data-usfm="PSA.7.11"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v12"
      data-usfm="PSA.7.12"><span class="label">12</span><span class="content">若有人不回头，他的刀必磨快，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v12" data-usfm="PSA.7.12"><span class="content">弓必上弦，预备妥当了。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v12" data-usfm="PSA.7.12"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v13"
      data-usfm="PSA.7.13"><span class="label">13</span><span class="content">他也预备了杀人的器械；</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v13" data-usfm="PSA.7.13"><span class="content">他所射的是火</span><span class="add"><span
        class="content">箭</span></span><span class="content">。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v13" data-usfm="PSA.7.13"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v14"
      data-usfm="PSA.7.14"><span class="label">14</span><span class="content">试看恶人因奸恶而劬劳，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v14" data-usfm="PSA.7.14"><span class="content">所怀的是毒害，所生的是虚假。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v14" data-usfm="PSA.7.14"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v15"
      data-usfm="PSA.7.15"><span class="label">15</span><span class="content">他掘了坑，又挖深了，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v15" data-usfm="PSA.7.15"><span class="content">竟掉在自己所挖的阱里。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v15" data-usfm="PSA.7.15"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v16"
      data-usfm="PSA.7.16"><span class="label">16</span><span class="content">他的毒害必临到他自己的头上；</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v16" data-usfm="PSA.7.16"><span class="content">他的强暴必落到他自己的脑袋上。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="b"></div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v16" data-usfm="PSA.7.16"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v17"
      data-usfm="PSA.7.17"><span class="label">17</span><span class="content">我要照着耶和华的公义称谢他，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v17" data-usfm="PSA.7.17"><span class="content">歌颂耶和华至高者的名。</span></span>
  </div>
</div>
